{"tid":2063023,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖] 罷免黃捷連署徵求理由，韓粉：看不順眼、翻白眼","createTime":"2020-06-13T14:36:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T15:25:00.000Z","uid":52658,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6414a3f880b5ad1bd5efc027971858e1b2c10716","tid":2063023,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T14:36:13.000Z","msg":"〔記者葛祐豪／高雄報導〕罷免黃捷連署展開，主辦單位稱連署份數已突破16000份，同時在網路上廣徵罷免理由，有韓粉竟說：「看不順眼」、「翻白眼」！<br />\n<br />\n發起罷免黃捷的「鳳山清&quot;捷&quot;大隊」王姓男子昨天在臉書上說，從6月8日連署以來，4天共計連署5000份，目前數量已經突破16000份（連同今年初已完成連署的11000份），所以將正式向中選會提出罷免申請。<br />\n<br />\n王姓男子並發起「罷免理由大徵選活動」，歡迎支持罷免黃捷的朋友，提出要罷免她的理由，將挑出10條，然後再來個民意調查，挑出前5條，作為正式罷免理由。<br />\n<br />\n底下留言的理由千奇百怪，例如「問政無能，只會賣弄風騷，無良心道德」、「離經叛道，撥弄是非」、「太會演戲，劇本脫離現實，質詢表現影響議會正常運作」等。也有韓粉直指罷免理由就是「看不順眼」、「翻白眼」。<br />\n<br />\n不過，根據高督盟去年評選出的高雄10大問政優質議員，黃捷就是其一，以「問政無能」為由要罷免她，恐無說服力。<br />\n<br />\n高雄地方政壇人士分析，「罷捷」過關機率微乎其微，就算通過一、二階連署，在第三階段的投票中，姑且不論同意票是否會過25%門檻，以黃捷在年輕及中間選民的高支持度，加上綠營基本盤聲援，不同意罷免票數絕對遠高於同意票數。<br />\n<br />\n政壇人士直言，黃捷是鳳山區選出的市議員，選議員時1萬8千多票就當選，但罷免走到第三階段投票時，雙方必定傾巢而出，以鳳山區公民人數29萬4千多人估算，屆時不同意罷免票數可能衝上10萬票，如果一舉衝破民進黨鳳山現任立委許智傑今年初的得票數11萬4998票，反而塑造出另一個政治明星，「最擔心的可能是許智傑了」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n時代力量議員黃捷<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kuJ3cs8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkuJ3cs8.jpg&h=ff8ab5ac&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xMKJWUP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxMKJWUP.jpg&h=3514d025&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DTDCgUQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDTDCgUQ.jpg&h=2a258adc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E1VQBUR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE1VQBUR.jpg&h=95b4c3f9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VRMz3zR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVRMz3zR.jpg&h=a0aa8e6b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"60dcb44b4d70790023a1caf864f524d98bd337ab","tid":2063023,"uid":91967,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T14:40:44.000Z","msg":"台妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2db6a7a9fe8c9e5d36b8630de60f86a085aa84b","tid":2063023,"uid":339805,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T14:41:34.000Z","msg":"好想同黃捷瘋狂做愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df4aee24487b784fc45b6d569aacd657231bf473","tid":2063023,"uid":52658,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2db6a7a9fe8c9e5d36b8630de60f86a085aa84b","tid":2063023,"uid":339805,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T14:41:34.000Z","msg":"好想同黃捷瘋狂做愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T14:46:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZMRwmqb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZMRwmqb.jpg&h=0c752878&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c2c9eb6e1171a63009c215a17d08b5335926298","tid":2063023,"uid":172497,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"a2db6a7a9fe8c9e5d36b8630de60f86a085aa84b","tid":2063023,"uid":339805,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T14:41:34.000Z","msg":"好想同黃捷瘋狂做愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T14:47:21.000Z","msg":"屌佢個口屌到入一入<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n瘋狂奶佢塊西<br />\n射爆佢對波"},{"pid":"00a9513906e78c97819524260dea1f1ba37924be","tid":2063023,"uid":17859,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T14:48:16.000Z","msg":"班韓狗唔係想罷蔡英文咩？<br />\n宜家做乜咁大個總統唔罷<br />\n搵個細粒嘅高雄市議員嚟罷？"},{"pid":"5488a6ae588e13e04e97a84ecadb74a3f73c9840","tid":2063023,"uid":47492,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00a9513906e78c97819524260d